    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kosmolaris</strong>  is a relaxing puzzle game where you'll have combine a wide variety of elements to create new ones, starting with four basic elements: <strong>Air</strong> 💨, <strong>Fire</strong>🔥, <strong>Earth</strong> 🍃 and <strong>Water</strong> 💧.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some elements are based on chemical principles, while others rely more on common sense or reverse engineering.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>There are two types of elements:</u> <strong>Common </strong>and <strong>Special</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Common: </strong>These are public knowledge, and you can unlock all of them without any restrictions, just by applying chemical principles and common sense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special:</strong> These are mainly <i>easter eggs</i>, and unlocking them may require specific knowledge about certain topics. They often aren't real elements but come from fictional sources or iconic moments from our lives and the world at large (possibly).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t worry if you don’t find them—they aren't the main goal of the game. But if you're curious...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Some features:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 languages for now: Spanish (Latam), Spanish (Spain), English, Italian, Portuguese and French.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outstanding elements art!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+200 common elements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+15 special elements (fiction, easter eggs).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+30 achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-save for each movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing background music.</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 法语, 意大利语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西",
